 Head of department
-Leading the Supply Chain Department; as people manager, Implements and Maintains a high quality mindset in the organization (supported by 5S/housekeeping), Manage staff to maximize motivation and involvement and minimize fluctuation
-Maintain a high level of technical knowledge in the organization to maximize productivity and quality in operations. Mapping and adopting team competence to address know-how gaps, and adopt future needs based on site development roadmaps. 
